rew rCtr(4) {1.0, (to dnsTGAddr from frsvAddr : response(1,('www844 . 'internet . 'com . 'root),nil,nil,nil,0) )} dnsTGenA3 .
>>
rCtr(4)
< dnsTGAddr : DNSTgen | qnameBase: 'internet . 'com . 'root, lenNameDB: 1000, retryTO: 5.0, retryMax: 2, dnsRsv: frsvAddr, nRetry: 2, numQ: 0, ctr: 2, w4: noQuery, replyTo: null > 
